Program: Start the Week
Title: 15/02/2010
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00qp09n
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 15 Feb 2010
Andrew Marr gains insight into the workings of government offices with the investigative journalist Michael Cockerell and the former MP Lord Hurd. Jonathan Miller gives a 19th-century Italian opera a 1950s American facelift, and Lyndall Gordon argues that it's time to look again at the life of the poet Emily Dickinson. Show less